# ── VITURE SDK binaries (download from https://www.viture.com/developer)
# Do NOT commit binary distributions; each developer fetches their own.
sdk/windows_x86_64/
sdk/linux_x86_64/
sdk/linux_aarch64/

# But DO keep the unified headers + license metadata
!sdk/include/
!sdk/LICENSE
!sdk/NOTICE
!sdk/README.md

